 THz\namplifiers or lasers is controlled by the incident optical pumping\n(photodoping) and the loaded dielectric materials in the HMM waveguide array,\nan interesting property that can have great potential for THz amplification,\nemission, and sensing applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Nov 2018 21:44:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 20:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-30"}
